records.title: New Woolworths Catalogue Arrived
records.body: A new Woolworths catalogue has been delivered to your letterbox. It has a QR code you can scan to get free samples, until out of stock or by 31/8/2017.

records.title: New Coles Catalogue Arrived
records.body: A new Coles catalogue has been delivered to your letterbox. It has a QR code you can scan to join an event with a chance to win a free gift.

records.title: Free Gift Won
records.body: You've won a free gift for the last event you've joined.
